{"word":"διαρραίω","slug":"διαρραίω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαρραίω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><p/><i>to dash in pieces, destroy</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a>, <i>to be destroyed, perish</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a>;</b> <el>διαρραισθέντας</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/>"}]}